headline: Has Dollar General’s 75% 2025 Rally Already Priced In Its Recovery Story?
summary: If you are wondering whether Dollar General is finally a bargain after a rough few years, or if the market has already priced in the recovery story, this breakdown will help you think through whether the current share price makes sense. After a painful multi year slide, the stock has roared back recently, climbing 20.9% over the last week, 33.4% over the past month, and 75.0% year to date, even though 3 year and 5 year returns remain deeply negative.
